org.gbif.common.parsers

Interface Parsable<TIN,TOUT>

  • Type Parameters:
    TIN - The input type of the parse operation
    TOUT - The output type of the parse operation
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BasisOfRecordParser, CountryNameParser, DictionaryBackedParser, FileBasedDictionaryParser, InterpretedCountryParser, InterpretedEnumParser, InterpretedLanguageParser, InterpretedRankParser, InterpretedTypeStatusParser, LanguageParser, RankParser, TypeStatusParser

    public interface Parsable<TIN,TOUT>
    Generic interface to allow multiple parser implementations.

      ParseResult<TOUT> parse(TIN input)

    • Method Detail

      • parse

        ParseResult<TOUT> parse(TIN input)
        Tries to parse the input and returns a ParseResult object. This should never return null as parse errors will be indicated in the returned object.
        Parameters:
        input - To parse
        Returns:
        The output result of the operation
